Class countryRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.countryRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class countryRecord
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This model is created for storing the Country Table properties.It includes a constructor(no arg and full arg), setter/getters for all properties and a tostring() method
